news.title: Noida authority razes 26 structures in four housing societies
news.para: The anti-demolition team deputed by the Authority, along with a police force, carried out the drive against illegal structures in two projects of AIMS Max Gardenia in Sector 75, Eldeco Amantram in Sector 119 and Homes 121 in Sector 121.

news.title: Mahindra Lifespaces to jointly develop 4.8-acre land parcel in Dahisar
news.para: The project will offer approximately 5 lakh sq. ft. of carpet area. Mahindra Lifespaces recently reported a consolidated net profit of Rs 13.23 crore for the quarter ended September 2021.

news.title: A month left, but no plan yet to bring down Supertech twin towers
news.para: On Wednesday, a meeting among officials of three different companies, Noida Authority and demolition experts from the US and UK was held. But none of the participants could come up with any concrete plan.
